text: Begoña Gumucio (born 14 January 1992) is a Chilean competitive sailor. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the women's 49erFX. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Chilean female sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Chile Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – 49erFX Category:Sailors at the 2015 Pan American Games
